<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَهُبُّ بِالنَّصْرِ ... فِي كُلِّ مَشْهَدْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنْعَمُ مِنَ الحُسْنَا ... بِكُلِّ حُسْنِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فِي الشّرف الاسنى ... وَظِلِّ أَمْنِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>يَا صِدْقَ مَنْ غَنَّى ... وَأَنْتَ تُغَنِّي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَا كَوْكَبُ المَجْدِ ... إِلَاّ مُحَمَّدْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَرَايَةُ الأَمْرِ ... عَلَيْهِ تُعْقَدْ ...<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>